headline: 3 Industrials Stocks with Questionable Fundamentals
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Sure, they are at the whim of macroeconomic factors that influence capital spending (like interest rates), but the industry has held its ground over the past six months as its 11.2% return was almost identical to the S&P 500.
